These are Puzzles for 2x6 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-8-1::.
The people's birthday is in 6 different months: february, october, july, december, august, april
There are 6 different favourite beverages: cola, iced-tea, soy-milk, milk, tea, almond-milk
 1. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1
 2. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left or right of the person drinking iced-tea##3
 3. the person who's birthday is in october is somewhere to the right of the person drinking cola##5
 4. the person drinking almond-milk is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in july##8
 5. the person who's birthday is in april is somewhere to the right of the person drinking tea##5
 6. the person drinking tea is somewhere between the person drinking soy-milk and the person who's birthday is in april##7
 7. the person who's birthday is in february is not to the left of the person drinking soy-milk##8
 8. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left or right of the person drinking iced-tea##3
 9. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in august##3
10. the person drinking cola is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in december##8
11. the person drinking tea is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in december##5
12. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the person who's birthday is in december##1
13. the person who's birthday is in july is somewhere to the right of the person drinking soy-milk##5
14. the person who's birthday is in april is somewhere between the person drinking iced-tea and the person who's birthday is in july##7
15. the person drinking almond-milk is somewhere to the right of the person drinking cola##5
16. the person who's birthday is in august is not the person drinking milk##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |   3    |   4   |       5        |   6   |
| Birthday           | december | october | february | august | april | july |
| Beverage   | cola | soy-milk    | iced-tea  | tea  | milk            | almond-milk  |

