.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-8-2::.
There 6 different types of food: cranberry, orange, kiwi, carrot, artichoke, zucchini
The people's birthday is in 6 different months: june, february, september, october, january, may
 1. the person eating carrot is not the person who's birthday is in may##6
 2. the person who's birthday is in may is in an even position##4
 3. the person who's birthday is in january is not to the right of the person who's birthday is in october##8
 4. the person eating kiwi is on the far left or far right##3
 5. the person who's birthday is in may is between the person eating carrot and the person who's birthday is in february##2
 6. the person who's birthday is in june is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in september##5
 7. the person who's birthday is in october is somewhere to the right of the person eating kiwi##5
 8. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in may##3
 9. the person eating orange is not the person who's birthday is in october##6
10. the person eating cranberry is on the far left or far right##3
11. the person eating artichoke is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in september##8
12. the person who's birthday is in may is not to the right of the person eating artichoke##8
13. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left or right of the person eating cranberry##3
14. the person eating zucchini is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1
15. the person who's birthday is in september is somewhere to the left of the person eating carrot##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |      2      |      3       |   4    |    5    |    6    |
| Food   | kiwi | zucchini | orange | artichoke | carrot | cranberry |
| Birthday     | september  | june  | february         | may | january    | october   |

