.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-8-3::.
City: san-francisco, prague, rome, liverpool, colone, nizza
House: ranch-style, tower, palace, townhouse, gothic-revival, colonial
 1. the tower house is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to rome##5
 2. the person traveling to prague is somewhere to the right of the tower house##5
 3. the colonial house is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to colone##5
 4. the palace house is not to the left of the person traveling to prague##8
 5. the person traveling to rome is somewhere to the left of the colonial house##5
 6. the person traveling to nizza is on the left or right of the person traveling to rome##3
 7. the ranch-style house is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to rome##5
 8. the person traveling to liverpool is not to the right of the person traveling to liverpool##8
 9. the person traveling to san-francisco is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to rome##5
10. the townhouse house is on the far right##1
11. the colonial house is somewhere between the person traveling to colone and the palace house##7
12. the tower house is somewhere to the left of the palace house##5
13. the person traveling to nizza is between the gothic-revival house and the colonial house##2
14. the person traveling to prague is on the right of the person traveling to liverpool##1
15. the palace house is somewhere between the colonial house and the person traveling to san-francisco##7
16. the gothic-revival house is not to the left of the gothic-revival house##8
17. the colonial house is somewhere to the right of the gothic-revival house##5
18. the person traveling to colone is the tower house##1
19. the palace house is not the person traveling to san-francisco##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3      |       4       |     5     |    6     |
| City   | colone   | rome | nizza    | liverpool      | prague | san-francisco |
| House         | tower | gothic-revival  | ranch-style | colonial | palace   | townhouse  |

