 2. the person who's birthday is in february is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in november##5
 3. the person who likes lilac is between the person who's birthday is in may and the person who likes red##2
 4. the person who likes brown is in an even position##4
 5. the person who likes lilac is somewhere between the person who likes yellow and the person who's birthday is in september##7
 6. the person who's birthday is in april is somewhere to the left of the person who likes turquise##5
 7. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in november##3
 8. the person who's birthday is in march is not to the left of the person who likes lilac##8
 9. the person who's birthday is in september is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in march##5
10. the person who's birthday is in april is somewhere to the left of the person who likes turquise##5
11. the person who's birthday is in march is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in november##5
12. the person who's birthday is in may is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in april and the person who likes lilac##7
13. the person who's birthday is in april is not to the right of the person who's birthday is in february##8
14. the person who likes turquise is on the left of the person who likes lavender##1
15. the person who's birthday is in april is in an even position##4
16. the person who likes lavender is in an even position##4
17. the person who's birthday is in september is somewhere to the left of the person who likes lilac##5

