.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-8-6::.
6 different pets are kept: frog, lizard, guinea-pig, horse, dog, goldfish
The people's birthday is in 6 different months: december, may, january, november, august, february
 1. the person who's birthday is in may is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in august##5
 2. the person who's birthday is in december is not to the left of the owner of the dog##8
 3. the owner of the frog is the person who's birthday is in january##1
 4. the owner of the lizard is somewhere to the left of the owner of the dog##5
 5. the person who's birthday is in february is the owner of the goldfish##1
 6. the owner of the horse is not to the right of the person who's birthday is in december##8
 7. the person who's birthday is in january is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in august##3
 9. the person who's birthday is in january is not to the right of the person who's birthday is in december##8
10. the owner of the dog is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1
11. the owner of the horse is not the person who's birthday is in november##6
12. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left or right of the owner of the horse##3
13. the owner of the horse is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
14. the person who's birthday is in august is somewhere to the left of the owner of the dog##5
15. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left of the person who's birthday is in august##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |  2  |   3   |     4     |  5   |    6    |
| Pet      | lizard | frog | guinea-pig  | horse     | goldfish  | dog  |
| Birthday   | november       | january | august | may | february | december |

