 4. the person drinking milk is on the left or right of the person eating spinach##3
 5. the person eating tomato is not to the right of the person eating garlic##8
 6. the person eating spinach is on the far left##1
 7. the person drinking cola is on the left or right of the person eating peas##3
 8. the person drinking soy-milk is not to the left of the person eating tomato##8
 9. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
10. the person drinking coffee is between the person eating lettuce and the person drinking cola##2

