 4. the fan of electronic is somewhere to the left of the person who growsiris##5
 5. the fan of pop is somewhere to the left of the fan of country##5
 6. the fan of house is not the person who growsorchid##6
 7. the fan of pop is on the right of the fan of electronic##1
 8. the fan of country is somewhere between the fan of hip-hop and the fan of electronic##7
 9. the person who growsiris is on the right of the person who growsorchid##1
10. the fan of house is on the left of the fan of country##1
11. the fan of house is not to the right of the person who growsorchid##8
12. the fan of dubstep is not to the left of the person who growspoppy##8
13. the person who growsiris is somewhere to the right of the fan of electronic##5
14. the person who growsazalea is somewhere between the person who growsbellflower and the person who growsorchid##7

.:: Answer ::.
