13. the person who likes ivory is on the far left or far right##3
14. the fan of punk is somewhere between the fan of salsa and the person who likes blue##7
15. the fan of salsa is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |   3    |    4     |     5      |      6      |
| Music-Genre   | salsa | punk | dubstep | pop   | hip-hop    | blues |
| Color   | mauve | lavender      | coral | chestnut | blue | ivory  |

